      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_5051">
            <h1 id="human-resources-director">Human Resources Director</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>The Director is responsible for leading the HR function within the FCO and its global network of 12,800 staff. They are a member of the FCO Management Board and the Civil Service HR Executive. The Director co-chairs the cross-Whitehall International People Board.</p>
</div>
